  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/456180/extras/46a2efb5ddd8740fd92474d9eadcbb03.avif?t=1747868753\" width=600 height=121 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Samurai Punk presents The American Dream, a satirical virtual reality trip to a ‘brighter future’ where your everyday needs are solved with guns. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/456180/extras/07bae19354dc8582d6de5d1577093107.poster.avif?t=1747868753\" width=602 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/456180/extras/07bae19354dc8582d6de5d1577093107.webm?t=1747868753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/456180/extras/07bae19354dc8582d6de5d1577093107.mp4?t=1747868753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's the 1950’s and a group of leading gun manufacturers have constructed a vast complex to guide the American Patriot towards a better and richer life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/456180/extras/7dd8090fb20baa4a586f81b342a925be.poster.avif?t=1747868753\" width=602 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/456180/extras/7dd8090fb20baa4a586f81b342a925be.webm?t=1747868753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/456180/extras/7dd8090fb20baa4a586f81b342a925be.mp4?t=1747868753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the talking dog Buddy Washington as your guide, you'll get to experience what it's like to live all aspects of your life with guns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/456180/extras/3427d4f4d2a4c6eedfc194e517416c5c.webp?t=1747868753\" width=600 height=53 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully-voiced, single player, narrative-driven campaign with over 20 unique levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn how guns can help improve the key moments of your life as an Average American.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience immersive, interactive environments ready to meet the business end of your weapons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A host of lovingly crafted firearms including pistols, shotguns, SMGs and tactical sporting rifles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bullets.<br>  </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/456180/extras/46a2efb5ddd8740fd92474d9eadcbb03.avif?t=1747868753\" width=600 height=121 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Samurai Punk presents The American Dream, a satirical virtual reality trip to a ‘brighter future’ where your everyday needs are solved with guns. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/456180/extras/07bae19354dc8582d6de5d1577093107.poster.avif?t=1747868753\" width=602 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/456180/extras/07bae19354dc8582d6de5d1577093107.webm?t=1747868753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/456180/extras/07bae19354dc8582d6de5d1577093107.mp4?t=1747868753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's the 1950’s and a group of leading gun manufacturers have constructed a vast complex to guide the American Patriot towards a better and richer life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/456180/extras/7dd8090fb20baa4a586f81b342a925be.poster.avif?t=1747868753\" width=602 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/456180/extras/7dd8090fb20baa4a586f81b342a925be.webm?t=1747868753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/456180/extras/7dd8090fb20baa4a586f81b342a925be.mp4?t=1747868753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the talking dog Buddy Washington as your guide, you'll get to experience what it's like to live all aspects of your life with guns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/456180/extras/3427d4f4d2a4c6eedfc194e517416c5c.webp?t=1747868753\" width=600 height=53 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully-voiced, single player, narrative-driven campaign with over 20 unique levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn how guns can help improve the key moments of your life as an Average American.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience immersive, interactive environments ready to meet the business end of your weapons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A host of lovingly crafted firearms including pistols, shotguns, SMGs and tactical sporting rifles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bullets.<br>  </p></li></ul>",
